Have you located the bicep tendon?

98
00:16:12,958 --> 00:16:14,458
Is it around here?

99
00:16:14,541 --> 00:16:17,708
Yes, look for it, so you can answer
Professor Suthee when he comes.

100
00:16:18,708 --> 00:16:19,958
