101
00:16:21,583 --> 00:16:25,541
Of course, I strictly followed
all the procedures.

102
00:16:27,708 --> 00:16:30,333
Look, here's the flexor
that Professor Suthee talked about.

103
00:16:30,541 --> 00:16:32,041
-It's right here.
-Where?

104
00:16:38,750 --> 00:16:40,916
-You idiot!
-You guys are shrieking like scaredy-cats.

105
00:16:49,250 --> 00:16:50,541
Hey, Dr. Jib.

106
00:16:51,375 --> 00:16:53,208
I have taught you to become
a medical professor.

107
00:16:53,458 --> 00:16:55,708
I didn't teach you to become friends
with those students.

108
00:16:57,291 --> 00:16:58,458
What's his name?

109
00:16:59,458 --> 00:17:01,541
His name is Siwapong, sir.

110
00:17:01,750 --> 00:17:02,833
Siwapong.

111
