What?

119
00:17:42,875 --> 00:17:44,041
I'm talking about Usa.

120
00:17:44,500 --> 00:17:46,666
We haven't seen each other in ages.

121
00:17:49,333 --> 00:17:50,875
Well, she's fine.

122
