131
00:18:37,583 --> 00:18:38,541
You can go now.

132
00:18:39,916 --> 00:18:41,291
Excuse me, then.

133
00:18:50,166 --> 00:18:52,041
Let me know when you have to be
on duty at night.

134
00:18:56,000 --> 00:18:57,333
-Aey.
-What?

135
00:18:57,416 --> 00:18:59,375
Let me know when you have to be
on duty at night.

136
00:18:59,833 --> 00:19:00,833
Why?

137
00:19:02,208 --> 00:19:03,875
It's so that I can find some company.

138
00:19:05,666 --> 00:19:06,791
Are you scared?

139
00:19:09,000 --> 00:19:12,541
It's pretty spooky around here,
but you'll get used to it soon.

140
00:19:17,375 --> 00:19:18,208
Chon.

141
00:19:19,666 --> 00:19:20,958
Did you see something?

142
00:19:23,166 --> 00:19:24,291
Hey.

143
00:19:24,375 --> 00:19:26,083
Don't do this.

144
00:19:26,250 --> 00:19:29,833
Really, someone got murdered
near the main road last week.

145
00:19:30,708 --> 00:19:32,916
I don't believe you.

146
00:19:33,000 --> 00:19:35,875
-How is that funny?
-You're such a chicken.

147
00:19:35,958 --> 00:19:37,208
So what?

148
00:19:37,541 --> 00:19:38,916
You're a sissy.

149
00:19:44,583 --> 00:19:46,166
-I'll put it right here.
-Okay.

150
00:19:53,166 --> 00:19:54,083
Hey.

151
00:19:54,833 --> 00:19:56,208
I wanted to ask you since you came in.

152
00:19:56,833 --> 00:19:58,375
-What is it?
-Whose car is that?

153
00:20:03,291 --> 00:20:04,666
It's the owner's car.

154
00:20:06,541 --> 00:20:07,791
He let you use the car?

155
00:20:09,000 --> 00:20:09,958
Yes.

156
00:20:10,625 --> 00:20:12,166
I hardly use it.

157
00:20:14,208 --> 00:20:15,125
He's very kind.

158
00:20:16,750 --> 00:20:17,958
I want to meet him in person.

159
00:20:18,208 --> 00:20:19,291
When is he coming again?

160
00:20:20,791 --> 00:20:22,041
He rarely comes.

161
00:20:23,333 --> 00:20:24,625
